name: AntiJoker
0:
”Alexa open anti joker”
”Alexa, ask anti joker to tell me an anti joke”
”Alexa, open anti joker and I want to hear an anti joke”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: anti joker
des:
When the user requests a joke, Alexa pulls an anti joke from a large set of pre-programmed anti-jokes.

An anti-joke, is a "a joke or riddle-joke that starts like a standard joke or riddle-joke, but then turns out not to be a joke at all. The surprise element thus becoming the joke."

Jokes are intended for all audiences and contain no suggestive themes or foul language.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
